OL,3,CThree remanded over alleged arson on
OL,4,CJewish group ambulances as new arrest
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FTwo young men and a boy have been
OL,8,Fremanded in custody after appearing in
OL,9,Fcourt accused of torching four Jewish
OL,10,Fcommunity ambulances in north-west
OL,11,FLondon.
OL,13,FThe ambulances from Hatzola, a
OL,14,Fvolunteer-led ambulance service
OL,15,Foperating in the Golders Green area of
OL,16,Fnorth-west London, were set on fire in
OL,17,Fthe early hours of March 23, causing
OL,18,Fgas canisters stored in the vehicles
OL,19,Fto explode, resulting in #1 million
OL,20,Fworth of damage, Westminster
OL,21,FMagistrates Court heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
