PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775426988
OL,3,CThree remanded over alleged arson on
OL,4,CJewish group ambulances as new arrest
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FBritish men Hamza Iqbal, 20, and Rehan
OL,8,FKhan, 19, from Leyton, east London,
OL,9,Fand a 17-year-old boy, of dual British-
OL,10,FPakistani nationality, from
OL,11,FWalthamstow, are each charged with one
OL,12,Fcount of arson being reckless as to
OL,13,Fwhether life would be endangered.
OL,15,FThe accused, who were arrested as part
OL,16,Fof a Counter Terrorism Policing (CTP)
OL,17,Finvestigation, did not enter pleas and
OL,18,Fwere remanded in custody during the
OL,19,Fhearing, which lasted around 45
OL,20,Fminutes on Saturday afternoon.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775426988
OL,3,CThree remanded over alleged arson on
OL,4,CJewish group ambulances as new arrest
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FThe court heard a fourth suspect was
OL,8,Farrested in connection with the
OL,9,Falleged arson at court on Saturday
OL,10,Fmorning.
OL,12,FProsecutor Emma Harraway told the
OL,13,Fcourt: "There is significant evidence
OL,14,Fthat this was a premeditated and
OL,15,Ftargeted attack against the Jewish
OL,16,Fcommunity."
OL,18,FProsecutors do not yet know the
OL,19,Fmotivation for the alleged attack,
OL,20,Fwhich "specifically targeted" the
OL,21,Fambulances, the court heard.
OL,26,@uD@HOUxD@KO]|D@GOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
