OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775426988
OL,3,CThree remanded over alleged arson on
OL,4,CJewish group ambulances as new arrest
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FThe case is not being treated as
OL,8,Fterrorism but CTP said due to "the
OL,9,Fcircumstances of the incident" the
OL,10,Finvestigation is being led by its
OL,11,Fdetectives.
OL,13,FThe defendants spoke only to confirm
OL,14,Ftheir personal details during the
OL,15,Fhearing, which took place before a
OL,16,Ffull public gallery of relatives.
OL,18,FAs Iqbal, who wore a grey prison-issue
OL,19,Ftracksuit in the dock, was taken to
OL,20,Fthe cells, a member of the public
OL,21,Fgallery said: "Take care son, yeah."
OL,26,@pD@_OUqD@^O]}D@OOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
