PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1775426988
OL,3,CThree remanded over alleged arson on
OL,4,CJewish group ambulances as new arrest
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FThe court heard Khan, who also wore a
OL,8,Fgrey prison-issue tracksuit, is a
OL,9,Fcollege student.
OL,11,FBoth were remanded into custody, with
OL,12,Fthe 17-year-old, who cannot be named
OL,13,Ffor legal reasons, remanded into youth
OL,14,Fdetention accommodation.
OL,16,FThe three defendants are set to appear
OL,17,Fat the Old Bailey on April 24.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
