OL,3,CThree remanded over alleged arson on
OL,4,CJewish group ambulances as new arrest
OL,5,Cmade
OL,7,FTwo other men aged 45 and 47 who were
OL,8,Farrested last week, and are also
OL,9,FBritish, were released on bail until
OL,10,Flate April.
